Tree Management System
├── 1. User Management
│   ├── 1.1 Admin Panel
│   │   ├── User Management
│   │   ├── Tree Nursery Management
│   │   ├── Reports & Dashboard Access
│   │   └── System Configuration
│   ├── 1.2 Farmer Portal
│   │   ├── Tree Request Submission
│   │   ├── View Tree Allocations
│   │   ├── Update Planting Status
│   │   └── Dashboard Access
│   └── 1.3 Staff Portal
│       ├── Tree Inventory Management
│       ├── Planting Site Monitoring
│       ├── Growth Information Update
│       └── Field Data Logging

├── 2. Tree Nursery Management
│   ├── 2.1 Tree Species Database
│   │   ├── Add/Edit/Delete Species
│   │   ├── View Species Details
│   │   └── Search/Filter Species
│   ├── 2.2 Inventory Management
│   │   ├── Add/Edit/Delete Inventory
│   │   ├── View Current Stock
│   │   ├── Track Distributed Trees
│   │   └── Manage Stock Levels
│   └── 2.3 Distribution Records
│       ├── Log Tree Distribution
│       ├── View Distribution History
│       └── Generate Distribution Reports

├── 3. Farmer Information Management
│   ├── 3.1 Farmer Database
│   │   ├── Add/Edit/Delete Farmer Details
│   │   ├── View Farmer Profiles
│   │   └── Search/Filter Farmers
│   ├── 3.2 Tree Request Portal
│   │   ├── Tree Request Form
│   │   ├── Track Request Status
│   │   └── Manage Farmer Requests
│   └── 3.3 Farmer Dashboard
│       ├── View Tree Allocations
│       ├── View Planting Status
│       └── Access Pending Requests

├── 4. Planting Site Monitoring
│   ├── 4.1 Planting Records
│   │   ├── Log Planting Activities
│   │   ├── Update Planting Data
│   │   └── View Planting History
│   ├── 4.2 GIS Integration
│   │   ├── Map Planting Sites
│   │   ├── Track Tree Growth
│   │   └── Monitor Survival Rates
│   └── 4.3 Growth Tracking
│       ├── Record Growth Data
│       ├── Provide Care Instructions
│       └── Generate Growth Reports

├── 5. Reporting & Dashboards
│   ├── 5.1 Nursery Dashboard
│   │   ├── Overview of Tree Stock
│   │   ├── Distribution Statistics
│   │   └── Inventory Summary
│   ├── 5.2 Planting Dashboard
│   │   ├── Areas Planted Overview
│   │   ├── Tree Type Statistics
│   │   └── Survival Rate Data
│   ├── 5.3 Farmer Dashboard
│   │   ├── View Farmer Data
│   │   ├── Tree Allocations Summary
│   │   └── Planting History
│   └── 5.4 Reports
│       ├── Generate Detailed Reports
│       ├── Export Reports (PDF/Excel)
│       └── Customizable Report Templates

├── 6. Tree Request Portal
│   ├── 6.1 Tree Request Form
│   │   ├── Specify Tree Types
│   │   ├── Enter Quantity Required
│   │   └── Submit Request
│   ├── 6.2 Request Status
│   │   ├── View Request Progress
│   │   └── Update Request Status
│   └── 6.3 Farmer Notifications
│       ├── Notify Farmers on Request Approval
│       ├── Notify Farmers on Tree Allocation
│       └── Notify Farmers on Delivery

└── 7. Mobile App (Optional)
    ├── 7.1 Farmer Access
    │   ├── Tree Request Submission
    │   ├── View Dashboard
    │   └── Update Planting Status
    └── 7.2 Field Monitoring
